@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_evluad(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = v0
    v1 = tmp
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.abs((v1 + 0.08 * v2 + 0.17)))
    tmp = (((v0 + 0.50 + v1 + 0.32) + (v1 + 0.85 / v0 + 0.06)) - 0.28)
    v2 = tmp
    v0 = (0.42 / wp.cos(wp.abs(v2 + 0.61)))
    data[tid] = v0
